<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page non trouvée - A Laiz Prod</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/style.css') }}">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-container">
            <div class="error-content">
                <div class="error-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
                </div>
                <h1>404</h1>
                <h2>Cette page a perdu le rythme !</h2>
                <p>La page que vous cherchez semble avoir quitté la scène. Mais ne vous inquiétez pas, notre musique continue !</p>
                
                <div class="error-actions">
                    <a href="{{ url_for('index') }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Retour à l'Accueil
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{ url_for('services') }}" class="btn btn-secondary">
                        <i class="fas fa-music"></i> Nos Services
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="error-suggestions">
                    <h3>Ou explorez directement :</h3>
                    <div class="suggestions-links">
                        <a href="{{ url_for('contact') }}"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Contact</a>
                        <a href="{{ url_for('about') }}"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> À Propos</a>
                        <a href="{{ url_for('formations') }}"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Formations</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="error-musical-note">
                <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D3748 0%, #4A5568 100%);
            color: #FEFEFE;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #D69E2E;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        .error-page h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D69E2E 0%, #ED8936 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .error-page h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #FEFEFE;
        }

        .error-page p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .error-suggestions h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #D69E2E;
        }

        .suggestions-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .suggestions-links a {
            color: #FEFEFE;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .suggestions-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(214, 158, 46, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .error-musical-note {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 20rem;
            color: rgba(214, 158, 46, 0.05);
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-15deg);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            60% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-page h1 { font-size: 6rem; }
            .error-page h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .error-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
            .suggestions-links { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
